      "review_summary": "This PR adds a Crabline-backed QA Lab channel driver, new QA profile channel-driver semantics, live-profile evidence merging, QA CLI flags, docs, tests, and a smoke-ci workflow lane.\n\nPR surface: Source +1609, Tests +879, Docs +19, Config +52, Other +2. Total +2561 across 28 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. Source inspection shows a high-confidence path: PR head smoke-ci selects Crabline, the local provider echoes the prompt marker into an outbound message, and the baseline scenario waits only for that marker; running the focused smoke-ci baseline on the PR head should demonstrate the false-positive proof path.",
